snippet.title: Euro Truck Simulator 2 - West Balkans Video Trailer
snippet.description:
Get ready to explore & haul a variety of loads through Albania, Bosnia and Herzegovina, Croatia, Kosovo, Montenegro, North Macedonia, Serbia, and Slovenia. Discover hidden gems, local industries, history, culture, cities, and more on the road ahead! 

Ready to go? Add it to your Steam Wishlist TODAY! 
https://store.steampowered.com/app/2004210/Euro_Truck_Simulator_2__West_Balkans/"

Stock Media provided by Cinematic_Design / Pond5
